text = "You turn back. You don't draw the light again.

\"I wonder what this was all for.\"

\"I can't just trust a sparkle without any context — and kill all these creatures.\"

Behind you, Pip's voice goes thin. \"Hero...? Hero, come back.\"

You keep walking."
